Directives:
ng-app <=> attaches the Application Module to the page
ng-controller <=> attaches given controller to the page
ng-show/ng-hide <=> show/hide element based on expression given
ng-repeat <=> foreach
ng-src = used for specifying source paths (i.e. img)

TOREAD
filters, e.g. {{  value | filter }}
currency, date, limitTo, orderBy...

